      "span_text": "In general, CPU-GPU is the most popular hybrid solution in the field of computer vision for its excellent performance.  However, most CPU-GPU heterogeneous systems are fabricated as computers or workstations, which have high power consumption and are not suitable for small-scale mobile robots."
